query:
SELECT u.email, t.name as company_name, t.id as tenant_id
FROM users u
JOIN tenants t ON u.tenantId = t.id
LEFT JOIN tenantSubscriptions ts ON ts.tenantId = t.id
WHERE ts.id IS NULL
ORDER BY u.id DESC;
